Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤原公任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然那麼優秀的公任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上呢 最近有位女子讓我略有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她便是那本《源氏物語》的作者 藤式部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種因天生沉鬱…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而充滿倦怠氣息的才女我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲弄起這種人會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把她當作光源氏深愛的妻子紫之上 會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是光源氏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種稱呼還是省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不符合角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人能被允許性騷擾 有的人卻不能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有去性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她生氣應該是怪我不尊重她的著作吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自我防衛的狡辯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是說了同樣的話 大概她會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊信 你憑什麼這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 去試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是要去哪裡呀 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣…紫這個稱呼實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湍流飛瀑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,660)}たきのおとは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經久雖未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,660)}たえてひさしく なりぬれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公任大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不趕快工作的話 文書積壓起來很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}なこそながれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(640,85)}盛名傳四海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拖拖拉拉到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}なほきこえけれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(640,85)}遐邇極乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤式部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 過來 按我說的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我來探望您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並向您致以我的謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 謝我什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上那個…我…把筆名從藤式部改成了紫式部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主要是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前…公任大人稱我為紫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在皇宮裡別人也都這麼稱我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託您的福 《源氏物語》的評價也在逐漸提高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要感謝您給予了我一個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道謝就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有助於你的創作自是再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作 放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位 你們好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤原定家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 Hello 我是宇都宮賴綱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道《源氏物語》吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為世界最古老長篇小說的它 創作於約一千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語 德語 法語 漢語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被翻譯成二十多種語言 在世界中廣為閱讀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫出這部傑作的 是被稱作紫式部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是略晚於清少納言 在宮中奉仕的女性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個懷有出色才情的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後續還沒寫好嗎 式部大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能催她 很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是處於低潮期啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不想再寫下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這華麗的地方 明明都應付不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫不經心寫出的故事受到好評
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為教導中宮彰子大人的女官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深陷入宮侍奉的囹圄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀式部 最近寫得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…幾乎寫不出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 慢工出細活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天皇也很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入低潮寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為眾人所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有壓力而更覺萎靡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抱以更多期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越有壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一陷入充滿絕望的地獄最終失敗的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫些什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對得起周圍人的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描寫角色們絢麗歡騰的宮中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一一描繪出如夢似幻的美好愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寫什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本沒打算寫成長篇的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想寫不倫之戀 隱忍的苦戀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如源氏對父皇的妃子藤壺抱有的愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為我也一直在想念著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也觸不可及的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現如今那個人在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那美好的總角之交
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤…藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險 藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 給你 香子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子如小鳥一般輕盈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰都堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起我來 一直在讀書學習 連絲毫空閒都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}潯陽江頭夜送客 楓葉荻花秋瑟瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 香子的漢詩已經讀得這麼流利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你這麼大的時候實在是讀不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了 你在學問上的素養
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個女子居然在讀漢詩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真難相信你這麼不知羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒羞沒羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 香子已經能讀漢詩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家孩子還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對女子來說學問只是負累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼不是男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓我一直遺憾得不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香子 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嘲笑我區區女子竟讀漢詩 不知羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把香子惹哭的傢伙 我絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰說的 我去揍他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不讓他們哭著道歉我絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話藤子又要被說沒點姑娘家的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們愛說就說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比男孩還聰明的你是我的驕傲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼的 藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 這次你又讀的什麼詩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白樂天的詩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝無法守護他那比花還可人的貴妃 無奈賜死的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事？詩裡也有故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是一個十分悲傷的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 香子也寫個故事看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 那個 我寫不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 你每天都讀那麼多書嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香子的話一定能寫好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常想讀一讀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能用假名寫的話一定能讀懂的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事 為藤子而寫的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太厲害了 香子 太好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能寫出這樣的故事 香子真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香子學習那麼用功 又能寫故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不遜於任何一個男子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們做個約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我憑腕力 你憑學識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要勝過男子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以嗤笑還擊那些認為女性沒有自由的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拉鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有藤子會理解我 讚美我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子和我 我和藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有藤子在就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得藤子伴我身側 其他皆可棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你要結婚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看對方還不錯 就定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是不能違抗父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不情不願地結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是決定了換個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想往哪兒發展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腕力已經贏不過男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有才情 能跟男人們媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一技之長的我怎樣才能贏那些男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮了好久終於
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定用 我的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把男人們玩弄於鼓掌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是從來都不示弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是為了父母的顏面 無法拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看似特立獨行 卻很孝順
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 當然我沒打算守在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方似乎也能同意我入宮出仕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能不把他當做我的踏板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再艱辛的事也能積極面對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想方設法去克服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你的這份 我身上不存在的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 讓我自豪的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是有遺憾的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚以後 我就得離開京城了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方要去地方任職
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我好想一直跟香子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果香子是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就絕對嫁過去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 為什麼我不是男的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給她帶去最大的幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我 是我最需要她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我最深地愛著她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子隨著丈夫 離開了京城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不久后我也結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但丈夫卻先棄我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我 侍於當今的中宮 彰子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那天以後 便再也沒見過藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子 快點回京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 您丈夫在這次的除目上被派去外地了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出了點頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 讓他一個人去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 這裡的工作才最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別每天晚上寂寞得以淚洗面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式部大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前提到過的兒時好友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫的任期結束 回到京城了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子她 回京了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 趕快去見一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫在這次的除目上被任命為甲斐守了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎近期就要舉家出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有告訴我啊 藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼地 這麼地想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 還是像以前一樣只會埋頭學習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我們當年所約
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能在才學上跟男人們平起平坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在寫小說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被天皇稱讚說有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 整天吵著架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好多好多的話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只想 只想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認錯人…了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那就是藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能認錯藤子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有一封給您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名為香子的大人寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真的是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像陰霾夜空中的明月一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為窺得其影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又躲藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五郎尿尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢 爸爸在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去情人那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道啊 真土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起 是媽媽不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼見你 香子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經走得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣 連怨言也說不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨著男人沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨不想 讓你看見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我憑腕力 你憑學識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要贏過男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只有我 堅持了過去的約定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子已經 放棄當時的心意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的心意一定沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是無法生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若她還抱著那樣的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅因為她是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在源氏物語中該寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是華貴的宮廷生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是如夢似幻的戀愛故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是女性的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婀娜而堅強的女性們的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我堅持寫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一天藤子就能讀到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓藤子看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個女性沒有自由的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能動搖她憔悴的心靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅強的女性們的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 香子一定能寫出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 香子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能寫出這麼棒的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香子好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把這份心意傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過你稱讚過的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫的小說的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來了源氏物語的續篇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請您過目嗎



